Dino Jump is a fun and addictive arcade game available as a Chrome extension. Take control of a cute dinosaur and help it jump over cacti and other obstacles. The goal is to see how far you can make the dinosaur jump without hitting anything. 

Tap the screen to make the dinosaur jump, timing your jumps perfectly to avoid obstacles and collect power-ups along the way. With its simple gameplay, charming graphics, and catchy sound effects, Dino Jump offers an enjoyable and challenging gaming experience. Compete against your own high scores or challenge friends to beat your record. Whether you're looking for a quick gaming session or a way to pass the time, Dino Jump provides endless fun right in your Chrome browser. Get ready to jump and have a dino-mite time!
